## Model preferences

# Set effort level and model via /model:
# - Set effort to High for all tasks (Boris's preference)
# - Use Opus with thinking for complex architectural work
# - Use Sonnet for standard coding tasks and subagents
# - Use Haiku for exploration-only agents (fastest, cheapest)

## Parallel workflow

# Boris runs 3-5 worktree sessions in parallel:
# - claude --worktree feature-auth   (session 1: auth feature)
# - claude --worktree fix-parsing    (session 2: bug fix)
# - claude --worktree add-tests      (session 3: test coverage)
#
# Tab naming convention: 1-feature, 2-tests, 3-bugfix
# Start mobile sessions from Claude iOS app, continue on desktop with --teleport
# Background sessions with & and check later

